{"tid":454310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共失國際化?  Coach專注NYSE擬撤回於本港聯交所上市","createTime":"2017-11-01T04:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T07:36:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14c5ce3b4f72e0b89f8bea95bd181e2907266888","tid":454310,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1362407_1_20171101110952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1362407_1_20171101110952.jpg&h=36d64fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTapestry Inc(前稱Coach)公布，已經向馬里蘭州財產評估及課稅部提呈並接納備存章程作出的修訂，並於本周二生效，反映公司名稱由「Coach, Inc.」更改為「Tapestry, Inc.」。公司普通股現時以股份代號「COH」於紐約證券交易所買賣，亦更改為「TPR」。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，公司表示，有意根據聯交所規則及法規申請撤回在香港發行的預託證券，從而撤回在聯交所主板上市，<br />\n原因是交投量偏低，以及為集中投放資源在第一上市地紐約證券交易所。"},{"pid":"0b442afe44fe3321551be48dbe3d4121cdba3e4d","tid":454310,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"實名化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc11bba6b96d81585568d45572512c08d529cb1","tid":454310,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}